'''方·愛德華·基墨'''（{{lang-en|Val Edward Kilmer}}，{{bd|1959年|12月31日||}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]男[[演員|演員]]。出生於[[加州|加州]][[洛杉磯市|洛杉磯市]]，{{link-en|好萊塢專業學校|Hollywood Professional School}}（Hollywood Professional School）畢業，17歲時以當時最年輕的錄取者進入[[茱莉亞音樂學院|茱莉亞音樂學院]]戲劇系就讀，曾因演出[[莎士比亞|莎士比亞]]名劇《[[哈姆雷特|哈姆雷特]]》而得獎。1986年因參與電影《[[捍衛戰士|-{zh-hans:壮志凌云;zh-hk:壯志凌雲;zh-tw:捍衛戰士;}-]]》（''Top Gun''）一片的演出而在電影界漸露頭角，代表作包括《[[永远的蝙蝠侠|永远的蝙蝠侠]]》（''Batman Forever''，1995年）、《[[神鬼至尊|神鬼至尊]]》（''The Saint''，1997年）等片。2022年再度參與電影《[[捍衛戰士：獨行俠|捍衛戰士：獨行俠]]》（''Top Gun: Maverick''）的演出。

== 个人生活 ==
2017年12月，《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》披露，基墨与“喉癌进行了为期两年的斗争”，“他[[氣管|氣管]]上的手术让他的声音变得沙哑，并使他呼吸急促”。为了说话，基墨在他的气管中插上了一个电声箱。<ref name="auto">{{cite web|last=Abramovitch|first=Seth|title=Val Kilmer Opens Up About Battling Cancer and His Kids' Showbiz Ambitions|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/val-kilmer-opens-up-battling-cancer-his-kids-showbiz-ambitions-1068733|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2017-12-20|access-date=2017-12-21|archive-date=2017-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220233102/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/val-kilmer-opens-up-battling-cancer-his-kids-showbiz-ambitions-1068733}}</ref>由于癌症，基墨接受了[[化学疗法|化疗]]和两次[[氣管切開術|氣管切開術]]。<ref name="auto"/><ref>{{cite web |last1=Pappademas |first1=Alex |title=Val Kilmer Doesn't Believe in Death |date=2020-04-21 |url=https://www.menshealth.com/trending-news/a32162764/val-kilmer-career-cancer-interview/ |publisher=Men's Health |access-date=2020-04-23 |archive-date=2020-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424030503/https://www.menshealth.com/trending-news/a32162764/val-kilmer-career-cancer-interview/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Day|first=Nate|date=2020-08-03|title=Val Kilmer says he's doing great after tracheotomy: 'I feel a lot better than I sound'|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/val-kilmer-doing-a-lot-better-after-tracheotomy|access-date=2020-08-05|website=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804123515/https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/val-kilmer-doing-a-lot-better-after-tracheotomy}}</ref><ref name="NYT_What_Happened">{{cite magazine |author1=Taffy Brodesser-Akner |title=What Happened to Val Kilmer? He's Just Starting to Figure It Out |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/05/06/magazine/val-kilmer.html |magazine=The New York Times Magazine |access-date=2020-08-14 |date=2020-05-06 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813224028/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/05/06/magazine/val-kilmer.html }}</ref>

2021年，经过复杂的工作，基墨的声音透過人工智能技术，利用他声音的音频档案重新再现出来。<ref>{{cite magazine|author1=Etienne Vanessa|title=Val Kilmer Gets His Voice Back for Top Gun:Maverick after Throat Cancer Battle Using AI Technology: Hear the Results|url=https://people.com/movies/val-kilmer-gets-his-voice-back-after-throat-cancer-battle-using-ai-technology-hear-the-results/|magazine=People.com|access-date=2021-08-19|date=2021-08-19|archive-date=2021-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819225905/https://people.com/movies/val-kilmer-gets-his-voice-back-after-throat-cancer-battle-using-ai-technology-hear-the-results/}}</ref>

